/*
** Name: play_NewOrder.h
**
** Description:
**      Defines the types used for the extension server functions
**
## History:
##      19-May-99 (fanra01)
##          Renamed SERVER_DLL_METHOD to SERVER_DLL_FUNCTION.
##          Add mt_safe_malloc, mt_safe_free and MEMORY_P
